arlut.csd.ganymede.common
Class adminAsyncMessage

java.lang.Object
  arlut.csd.ganymede.common.adminAsyncMessage
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class adminAsyncMessage
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

The adminAsyncMessage class is used by the Ganymede server to pass asynchronous messages to the Ganymede admin console. The Ganymede console repeatedly calls arlut.csd.ganymede.server.serverClientAsyncResponder#getNextMsgs() to receive asynchonous notifications from the server.
